headline: Henry Schein Expands Partnership with vVARDIS
summary: MELVILLE, N.Y., December 01, 2025--Henry Schein, Inc. (Nasdaq: HSIC) today announced the expansion of its agreement with vVARDIS, which grants the Company exclusive U.S. distribution rights for the drill-free Curodont™ Repair Fluoride Plus ("Curodont") product across all dental market segments, effective January 1, 2026.
